      • contains

        public static boolean contains(int buttonState,
                               int code)
        パラメータ:
        buttonState - Returned value from FrameInput#getButtonPressed(), FrameInput#getButtonReleased() or FrameInput#getButtonState().
        code - JoyButton.BUTTON_* constant value.
        戻り値:
        true if buttonState contains code in bit flags.
